info.name: Attendee : Student Portal
info.description:
The documentation is for the developers of Attendee app. All the requests are directly hit all the public routes.

| Requests | Working |
| --- | --- |
| Login | Yes |
| Forgot Password | Yes |
| Student Details | Yes |
| Result | Yes |
| Change Password | Yes |
| Subjects | Yes |
| Time Table | Yes |
| Regd. Code | Yes |
| Attendance | **No** |
